Day 46 — ROC Curve & AUC

📌 Overview

On Day 46, I learned ROC Curve and AUC, important metrics for evaluating classification models.

🧠 What I Learned

ROC Curve Concept

True Positive Rate (TPR)

False Positive Rate (FPR)

AUC (Area Under Curve)


📈 ROC Curve

ROC Curve plots:

TPR (Recall) vs FPR


TPR = \frac{TP}{TP + FN}

FPR = \frac{FP}{FP + TN}

🎯 AUC (Area Under Curve)

AUC = 1 → Perfect Model

AUC = 0.5 → Random Model

Higher AUC → Better Model


💡 Key Takeaway

ROC Curve helps evaluate classification performance across different thresholds.
